{
  "stem": "27335.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, well, right-- right there in Leduc-- I'm not-- not really knowing exactly, because my-- my profession was that I was an organizer at that time-- a professional organizer-- for our-- our movement, our organization.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came down for a convention which was planned for October, to be held in Hamilton.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they called me down early-- a month early-- to help to organize the convention.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I arrived here on a CPR train on-- on Saturday morning, that was-- it was 28th of August, 1939.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the exhibition was still on the last day, there was no exhibition of Sundays.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took me out to see the exhibition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then came Sunday, the 31st of August-- and they did put up-- put me up with a Hungarian family there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Monday morning, I was going down to the-- to the editorial office, and all-- all of a sudden, I had a call-- Andy!",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Andy!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there I see [NON-ENGLISH] a Hungarian guy, who was in our organization-- I already knew him-- he was delivering bread, you see.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, do know what-- what-- what the news is?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, the war broke out-- at 4 o'clock, a German invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
